 FEATURES
 --------

  It's allow you to have new button gadget for the bgui.library.

  This gadget can have:

    - a  width  smaller  than  the  label-text,
    - a justification on the label,
    - Change the label contents on the fly.
    - Change the colors (pen, background..) on the fly too.


  For more informations see the ButClass.doc.
